According to traffic alerts circulating on social media, the Waterval Boven tunnel has been blocked by rockfalls at both entrances as well as Schoemanskloof at De Beers Nek. Two trucks have also crashed into the rockfalls at Waterval Boven. The alternative routes suggested from Mbombela towards Middelburg includes Badplaas, Carolina as well as joining the N4 at Wonderfontein. From Kruger Gate, motorists are advised to use the Sabie, Longtom Pass and Lydenburg roads. 